        "custom_liquid_QjDbaD": {
          "type": "custom_liquid",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"mahekh-review-slider\">\n\n    <div class=\"review-header\">\n        ⭐ Trusted Customer Reviews\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-track\" id=\"reviewTrack\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Rahul Sharma <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Absolutely amazing fragrance. Lasted for more than 10 hours. Premium quality attar.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Aman Verma <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Very smooth and luxurious scent. Packaging was excellent.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Rohit Singh <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>One of the best attars I have purchased online. Highly recommended.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Arjun Mishra <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Elegant musk fragrance. Received compliments throughout the day.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Vivek Tiwari <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>The scent profile feels rich and premium. Worth every penny.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Nitin Yadav <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Long-lasting fragrance with a sophisticated aroma. Loved it.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Saurabh Pandey <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Beautiful blend. Smells expensive and unique.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Deepak Gupta <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Yaar fragrance bahut premium hai. Pure din kapdo me mehak bani rahi.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Ankit Srivastava <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Packaging aur fragrance dono top class nikle. Paisa vasool.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <div class=\"review-name\">Shubham Tripathi <span class=\"verified\">✔ Verified Buyer<\/span><\/div>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n            <p>Kasturi attar ki quality expected se bhi better nikli. Bahut badhiya.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.mahekh-review-slider{\n    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fffdf7,#fff8ea);\n    border:1px solid #e6d4a3;\n    border-radius:18px;\n    padding:20px;\n    overflow:hidden;\n    margin:20px 0;\n    position:relative;\n}\n\n.mahekh-review-slider::before{\n    content:'';\n    position:absolute;\n    top:0;\n    left:-100%;\n    width:100%;\n    height:100%;\n    background:linear-gradient(\n        90deg,\n        transparent,\n        rgba(255,255,255,0.35),\n        transparent\n    );\n    animation:shine 5s infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes shine{\n    100%{\n        left:100%;\n    }\n}\n\n.review-header{\n    text-align:center;\n    font-size:22px;\n    font-weight:700;\n    color:#222;\n    margin-bottom:20px;\n}\n\n.review-track{\n    display:flex;\n    gap:15px;\n    width:max-content;\n    animation:scrollReviews 45s linear infinite;\n}\n\n.review-track:hover{\n    animation-play-state:paused;\n}\n\n.review-card{\n    width:320px;\n    min-width:320px;\n    background:#ffffff;\n    border-radius:16px;\n    padding:18px;\n    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n    border:1px solid #f2ead0;\n}\n\n.review-name{\n    font-size:15px;\n    font-weight:700;\n    color:#222;\n    margin-bottom:10px;\n}\n\n.verified{\n    background:#e8f7ed;\n    color:#0a8f3e;\n    padding:4px 8px;\n    border-radius:30px;\n    font-size:11px;\n    font-weight:700;\n    margin-left:5px;\n    white-space:nowrap;\n}\n\n.stars{\n    color:#ffb400;\n    font-size:18px;\n    margin-bottom:10px;\n    letter-spacing:1px;\n}\n\n.review-card p{\n    font-size:14px;\n    line-height:1.6;\n    color:#555;\n    margin:0;\n}\n\n@keyframes scrollReviews{\n    0%{\n        transform:translateX(0);\n    }\n    100%{\n        transform:translateX(-50%);\n    }\n}\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n\n.review-card{\n    width:280px;\n    min-width:280px;\n}\n\n.review-header{\n    font-size:18px;\n}\n\n.review-card p{\n    font-size:13px;\n}\n\n}\n<\/style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function(){\n\n    const track = document.getElementById(\"reviewTrack\");\n\n    if(track){\n        track.innerHTML += track.innerHTML;\n    }\n\n});\n<\/script>"
          }
